mg_huge_tv-tower_v1 Made by Xylon, the map contain:

-64 spawns (32 CT spawns and 32 T spawns)
-2 Elevators
-The tower has 4 floors
-ladders protection (to prevent jump glitch)
-Every roofs have a fence to protect the player from falling down to death


Credit:
